    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "AIRCAL\nSYSTEM TIMETABLE\nEffective January 15, 1984\nNEW SERVICE\nPALM SPRINGS\nLos Angeles • Sacramento",
      "AIRCAL NOW THE MOST\nCONVENIENT AIRLINE AT LAX\nJanuary, 1984 marks the opening of AirCal's new facility in\nTerminal One, conveniently located at the entrance to Los\nAngeles International Airport. New two-tiered roadways have\nbeen constructed to make arrivals and departures fast and\neasy. Passengers will appreciate the new multilevel parking\nstructures located directly across from the AirCal terminal.\nAirCal and the New LAX.\nWe Make Flying Easy.\nTHENEW\nAIRCAL\nTERMINAL 1\nPARKING*\nLOT 1\nEffective January 23, 1984"
